title: Chris Brown’s daughter shows incredible dance moves at photo shoot
text:
Other Articles Magnetic energy can affect brain's perception of God Study sheds light on culinary habits of Stonehenge builders 'Fantasy Island' to get reboot with female protagonist Chris Brown’s daughter Royalty seems to be following her daddy’s footsteps, especially, when it comes to getting down.
The 26-year-old rapper was recently accompanied by his 17-month-old baby girl for a photo shoot for his upcoming album named on his daughter’s name, reports E! Online.
Brown posted a video on his Instagram, wherein his little one is seen showing some incredible dance moves while he stands behind her and smiles.
Previously, the ‘Loyal’ hit-maker announced that he will be dropping his album on November 27.
 14, 2015 8:30 pm
